-- Admati Says Banks Have Problem With `Will' to Lend (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-04-02T16:20:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-02/admati-says-banks-have-problem-with-will-to-lend-audio-.html
Anat Admati, the author of "The 
Bankers' New Clothes," says banks do not have a problem with 
lending money, they have a problem with the "will" to lend 
money. Admati spoke to Bloomberg's Carol Massar and  Matt Miller  
on "Bloomberg On the Economy."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 14:24
 